.TH BLUETOOTH-AUTOCONNECT 1 "June 2026" "ubuntu-cix-settings" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
bluetooth-autoconnect \- connect trusted Bluetooth devices
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bluetooth-autoconnect
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bluetooth-autoconnect
connects trusted Bluetooth devices through BlueZ. It can run once or stay in
daemon mode to reconnect devices when adapters or device state changes.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-d, \-\-daemon
Monitor Bluetooth adapters and reconnect trusted devices automatically.
.TP
.B \-v, \-\-verbose
Print verbose status messages.
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show command usage.
